---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms of Service - 1099TaxEst">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
		<div class="fintech-card p-8 prose prose-slate max-w-none">
			<p><strong>Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</strong></p>
			<h2>Usage and Disclaimer</h2>
			<p>By using 1099TaxEst, you agree to these terms. This tool provides simplified estimates for educational and informational purposes only. It is <strong>NOT</strong> official financial or tax advice.</p>
			<p>Tax laws are complex and subject to change. The calculator uses generalized 2024 Federal tax brackets and standard deductions. It does not account for State/Local taxes, the Qualified Business Income (QBI) deduction, or other specific credits you may be eligible for.</p>
			<h2>Limitations of Liability</h2>
			<p>We are not liable for any financial decisions, underpayment penalties, or miscalculations resulting from the use of this tool. Always consult a certified CPA or tax professional for your actual tax filings.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
